The EFF is promising to tackle gender-based violence. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The EFF is promising to tackle gender-based violence. The party says crimes against women and children must come to an end. READ: EFF will changes lives of poor in Mpumalanga: Malema EFF leader Julius Malema was speaking at the EFF's sixth birthday celebration in Mpumalanga on Saturday. “I have a big problem with you South Africans, your hatred for women is a problem for me. These crimes against our beautiful African women must come to an end. Why do you declare war against women? Why do you hate women?” he said.